text.div:
Vaccine Administered Code Set (CVX)

http://hl7.org/fhir/sid/cvx

The CDC's National Center of Immunization and Respiratory Diseases developed and maintains the CVX (vaccine administered) code set. It includes both active and inactive vaccines available in the US.
